addresses.description: The `Address` type. You can choose from `Address`, `BusinessAddress`, `MaillingAddress`, and `ShippingAddress`.

attributeMatchingModel.description: Configures the `AttributeMatchingModel`, you can either choose `ONE_TO_ONE` or `MANY_TO_MANY`.

emailAddresses.description: The `Email` type. You can choose from `EmailAddress`, `BusinessEmailAddress` and `PersonalEmailAddress`.

phoneNumbers.description: The `PhoneNumber` type. You can choose from `PhoneNumber`, `HomePhoneNumber`, and `MobilePhoneNumber`.
